WEBVTT

01:51.600 --> 01:57.520
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.750 --> 02:01.950
[Episode 1]

02:03.350 --> 02:04.350
Legend has it

02:04.350 --> 02:06.950
that in a remote southeastern corner,
far from the central lands,

02:06.950 --> 02:08.310
disasters plagued the region
year after year,

02:08.310 --> 02:10.680
and the common people lived in misery.

02:10.680 --> 02:13.710
At that time, a towering hero emerged.

02:13.710 --> 02:15.150
Both brave and wise,

02:15.150 --> 02:16.810
he brought order to the realm.

02:16.890 --> 02:19.450
With the support of the 9 families—

02:19.480 --> 02:21.060
Qi, Zheng, Fan, Wei, and others—

02:21.060 --> 02:22.650
he planned with foresight

02:22.680 --> 02:25.120
and carved out an era of prosperity.

02:25.720 --> 02:28.070
He was the co-lord of the Nine Cities,

02:28.090 --> 02:29.220
Qi Hua.

02:29.690 --> 02:31.800
The 9 families who aided him back then

02:31.829 --> 02:34.160
are the very Nine Noble Families of today.

02:34.540 --> 02:35.780
Thirteen years ago,

02:35.800 --> 02:37.630
the mayor was struck by a grave illness.

02:37.630 --> 02:39.240
His sons fought for succession,
plunging the land into chaos again.

02:39.240 --> 02:42.310
Once again, the Nine Noble Families
stepped in to restore order,

02:42.310 --> 02:44.840
but at a devastating cost,
suffering heavy casualties.

02:44.840 --> 02:45.630
In the end,

02:45.630 --> 02:47.800
only the youngest son,

02:47.800 --> 02:49.280
Qi Zheng, remained.

02:49.280 --> 02:51.880
The Nine Noble Families earned
the admiration of the people,

02:51.880 --> 02:55.340
and their stories have been passed down
through generations.

03:01.560 --> 03:06.060
[Fan Yun, the Young Lady
of the Fan Family]

03:11.090 --> 03:12.300
And so,

03:12.330 --> 03:14.370
in gratitude for their sacrifices,

03:14.400 --> 03:16.910
the common folks named the land
beneath their feet the "Nine Cities."

03:16.910 --> 03:17.750
Teacher! Teacher!

03:17.750 --> 03:19.000
I have another question.

03:19.000 --> 03:19.750
Go ahead.

03:20.280 --> 03:22.310
Then, is the current mayor

03:22.310 --> 03:24.010
a qualified mayor?

03:24.910 --> 03:26.630
You mean Qi Zheng?

03:33.600 --> 03:34.920
I believe

03:34.940 --> 03:36.620
a qualified mayor

03:36.650 --> 03:38.750
must be diligent in governance

03:38.990 --> 03:41.120
and personally attend to all affairs.

03:41.210 --> 03:42.450
[Huiyun Pavilion]

03:51.829 --> 03:55.800
[Mayor, Qi Zheng]

03:55.840 --> 03:57.120
Today, the sky is clear

03:57.120 --> 03:58.630
and the air is refreshing—

03:59.360 --> 04:02.560
perfect for reading documents
and reviewing memorials.

04:05.560 --> 04:06.310
Yan Jiang.

04:07.700 --> 04:08.300
Yan Jiang!

04:10.600 --> 04:11.440
Yan Jiang!

04:17.829 --> 04:19.940
[Yan Jiang, Assistant Officer
of the Bureau of Affairs]

04:21.160 --> 04:22.390
I'll leave

04:22.390 --> 04:23.800
these tasks to you.

04:24.120 --> 04:25.120
These? I...

04:25.120 --> 04:26.000
Yan Jiang.

04:26.720 --> 04:29.040
Yan Jiang, your writing flows
with brilliance—every word like a gem.

04:29.040 --> 04:30.290
You'll surely complete the tasks

04:30.290 --> 04:31.650
I've assigned you

04:31.680 --> 04:33.200
in one smooth, masterful sweep.

04:33.200 --> 04:34.860
I have full confidence in you.

04:35.070 --> 04:35.800
Wait.

04:36.370 --> 04:37.130
My Lord.

04:37.159 --> 04:38.600
This isn't how the idioms
are supposed to be used.

04:38.600 --> 04:39.190
Also,

04:39.210 --> 04:40.090
you are the mayor.

04:40.090 --> 04:43.150
These memorials should be reviewed
by you personally.

04:43.810 --> 04:45.180
You and I are as close as brothers.

04:45.180 --> 04:46.500
It makes no difference who handles them.

04:46.500 --> 04:48.159
Have confidence in yourself.

04:50.870 --> 04:51.340
But...

04:53.250 --> 04:55.090
Don't let me down.

04:55.120 --> 04:56.120
I believe in you.

04:57.640 --> 04:58.770
Where are you going?

04:58.780 --> 04:59.820
To relax for a bit.

05:02.160 --> 05:03.400
Teacher. Teacher.

05:03.420 --> 05:06.100
If the current mayor
had a teacher like you,

05:06.130 --> 05:07.660
he'd surely be able to do it.

05:10.110 --> 05:12.080
If one day

05:12.100 --> 05:13.850
I become the mayor's teacher,

05:14.190 --> 05:15.190
I'll make sure he governs with diligence

05:15.190 --> 05:17.790
and works for the well-being
of all the people.

05:18.080 --> 05:18.870
As for you,

05:18.890 --> 05:20.570
make sure you study hard

05:20.600 --> 05:23.090
to make the Nine Cities
stronger and better.

05:23.120 --> 05:23.850
Understand?

05:24.010 --> 05:25.730
-Understood.
-Understood.

05:27.420 --> 05:27.980
Gao Ran?

05:28.010 --> 05:30.280
-Mr. Gao Ran.
-Mr. Gao Ran.

05:29.260 --> 05:31.190
[Gao Ran, the Fan Family's Adopted Son]

05:33.320 --> 05:34.520
You must all be hungry.

05:34.520 --> 05:35.190
Come here.

05:36.630 --> 05:37.830
Mr. Gao Ran.

05:37.830 --> 05:39.159
What did you bring?

05:39.159 --> 05:40.360
-I want some too.
-I want some too.

05:40.360 --> 05:41.750
-Take it slow.
-Mr. Gao Ran!

05:41.750 --> 05:43.680
-Careful.
-Thank you, Mr. Gao Ran.

05:44.070 --> 05:45.200
Everyone gets some.

05:45.430 --> 05:46.290
I want some too.

05:46.290 --> 05:47.810
Here, be careful.

05:48.890 --> 05:50.150
Thank you, Mr. Gao Ran.

05:53.500 --> 05:54.640
Class is over for today.

05:54.640 --> 05:55.930
Hurry home, everyone.

05:55.960 --> 05:58.720
Goodbye, Teacher.

05:59.510 --> 06:01.040
Let's go home.

06:01.300 --> 06:02.510
Let's go. Hurry.

06:04.660 --> 06:05.580
Fan Yun.

06:05.610 --> 06:07.010
I'm here to take you home.

06:07.700 --> 06:08.790
Let's go home too.

06:16.690 --> 06:19.160
Go ahead, what's the agenda today?

06:19.190 --> 06:20.720
I'll just second it.

06:25.660 --> 06:26.990
The ancients once said,

06:27.390 --> 06:30.270
"a wife is a husband's greatest support."

06:27.420 --> 06:30.080
[Lyu Wenzhong, One of
the Three Elders of Nine Cities]

06:30.670 --> 06:33.060
[Zheng Yuan, Master of the Zheng family,
One of the Three Elders of Nine Cities]

06:32.390 --> 06:34.480
Yet look at our mayor—
since coming of age,

06:34.480 --> 06:36.340
he's been holding selections
for a wife every year,

06:36.340 --> 06:38.030
but to no avail.

06:38.920 --> 06:41.240
[Zhao Chang, One of
the Three Elders of Nine Cities]

06:40.070 --> 06:41.330
As the old saying goes,

06:41.360 --> 06:43.620
"cross that bridge when one comes to it."

06:43.830 --> 06:45.190
But now the bridge

06:46.000 --> 06:47.159
is broken.

06:49.420 --> 06:51.659
So, in your opinion, Lord Lyu,

06:52.190 --> 06:55.120
you think the mayor should start a family

06:55.720 --> 06:56.600
before

06:57.090 --> 06:58.560
pursuing his great cause?

06:58.930 --> 07:00.360
Exactly.

07:01.600 --> 07:02.950
Let's find

07:02.970 --> 07:04.850
a virtuous wife for the mayor

07:05.200 --> 07:08.850
who can subtly and positively
influence him.

07:09.750 --> 07:10.430
I think...

07:10.430 --> 07:13.160
Wait, let me finish.

07:13.810 --> 07:15.250
Perhaps

07:15.270 --> 07:18.270
it will be of great benefit to the mayor.

07:19.110 --> 07:19.770
That's all.

07:19.770 --> 07:20.900
You're done, right?

07:20.950 --> 07:23.510
I say we stop discussing it here.

07:23.510 --> 07:26.310
Let's just pick one for the mayor
and be done with it.

07:26.310 --> 07:27.220
Lord Zhao,

07:27.220 --> 07:30.260
you truly are
a veteran of the battlefield.

07:30.580 --> 07:30.950
Look at you...

07:30.950 --> 07:32.380
Don't you know

07:32.380 --> 07:34.260
that there are already rumors going around

07:34.260 --> 07:36.340
saying that we 3 old men

07:36.340 --> 07:38.460
have been sidelining the mayor,

07:38.690 --> 07:40.030
and that's why

07:41.300 --> 07:44.030
he's been neglecting state affairs?

07:45.570 --> 07:47.300
Is that so?

07:48.070 --> 07:49.190
Then, Lord Lyu,

07:49.700 --> 07:51.700
do you have a candidate in mind?

07:56.240 --> 08:04.550
[Fan Residence]

08:03.750 --> 08:06.380
I owe so much rent for
this private school.

08:06.380 --> 08:07.810
It's so frustrating.

08:13.240 --> 08:14.730
If only this house

08:15.140 --> 08:17.050
were worth more.

08:21.110 --> 08:22.020
I'm so poor.

08:30.640 --> 08:33.970
-He blew up the kitchen again.
-He blew up the kitchen again.

08:46.000 --> 08:48.060
[Fan Qi, Manager of Qilin Pavilion]

08:53.820 --> 08:54.460
Father!

08:54.460 --> 08:55.150
-Lord Fan Qi.
-Is the pot alright?

08:55.150 --> 08:55.950
Don't come over!

08:55.950 --> 08:56.910
I can do it!

08:56.910 --> 08:59.460
You may be able to hold on,
but this kitchen can't anymore.

08:59.460 --> 09:01.150
Father, how many times has this been?

09:01.150 --> 09:02.340
Come here!

09:02.340 --> 09:04.670
Let me check my pot. Did you...

09:05.630 --> 09:07.910
Did you burn another hole in it, Father?

09:10.910 --> 09:12.220
Dear father,

09:12.580 --> 09:14.820
you must be a pot seller's best customer.

09:14.820 --> 09:15.190
Well,

09:15.190 --> 09:18.390
I just wanted to make tea.

09:18.390 --> 09:19.220
I didn't expect it to end up like this.

09:19.220 --> 09:20.790
Who's this important guest that even

09:20.790 --> 09:22.270
our Lord Fan Qi—
who neither exercises

09:22.270 --> 09:25.030
nor knows his crops,
has to make tea for them himself?

09:25.030 --> 09:26.270
It's Lord Lyu.

09:26.820 --> 09:28.150
Is he important enough?

09:28.390 --> 09:29.670
-Lord Lyu?
-Lord Lyu?

09:40.100 --> 09:40.950
Lord Lyu,

09:40.950 --> 09:42.460
please have some tea.

09:49.220 --> 09:49.980
Father.

09:50.670 --> 09:52.910
Don't tell me
you just used this well water

09:52.910 --> 09:54.750
to make tea for Lord Lyu.

10:00.310 --> 10:01.070
Lord Lyu.

10:01.070 --> 10:01.770
Warm tea.

10:02.500 --> 10:03.300
Please enjoy.

10:13.790 --> 10:15.790
I wonder what brings you here today,

10:15.790 --> 10:17.190
Lord Lyu?

10:18.740 --> 10:21.790
There is something I need your help with.

10:23.100 --> 10:24.980
If you are willing to accept it,

10:26.840 --> 10:28.950
the reward is 500 taels of gold.

10:30.400 --> 10:32.190
This 50 taels is a deposit.

10:36.310 --> 10:37.060
I accept.

10:37.310 --> 10:38.910
Just tell me what you need.

10:38.910 --> 10:39.460
Anything.

10:39.460 --> 10:40.620
F-Fan Yun.

10:41.910 --> 10:42.430
Miss Fan.

10:42.430 --> 10:43.030
Come on. Come on.

10:43.030 --> 10:44.610
Come sit, and let's talk.

10:44.910 --> 10:46.570
I want to discuss with you guys

10:47.560 --> 10:48.330
to let Fan Yun

10:48.360 --> 10:50.310
enter the Qi Residence,

10:50.910 --> 10:52.340
marry the mayor

10:52.340 --> 10:54.270
and become his wife,

10:55.860 --> 10:58.590
and Gao Ran will be specially
granted permission

10:59.280 --> 11:01.620
to enter the Qi Residence
as the Head of Guardian Corps.

11:01.620 --> 11:02.870
L-L-Lyu...

11:03.150 --> 11:04.130
Lord Lyu.

11:04.500 --> 11:05.390
This matter...

11:06.390 --> 11:07.520
Is non-negotiable.

11:08.800 --> 11:10.820
This matter is non-negotiable, indeed.

11:10.820 --> 11:11.820
Wait, but...

11:43.150 --> 11:44.430
You scared me.

11:44.430 --> 11:45.430
Why are you hiding here

11:45.430 --> 11:46.820
drinking alone?

11:49.930 --> 11:51.910
I have something to discuss with you.

11:51.910 --> 11:52.860
Let's go visit their residence tomorrow

11:52.860 --> 11:54.320
and return all the gold...

11:55.030 --> 11:55.820
No.

11:56.590 --> 11:57.470
Why?

11:58.410 --> 12:01.170
Lord Lyu wants me
to enter the mayor's residence

12:01.200 --> 12:03.350
to influence him in a positive way.

12:03.460 --> 12:05.720
Since I've always wanted to be an official
since I was little,

12:05.720 --> 12:07.270
we might as well enter that residence
and check it out.

12:07.270 --> 12:09.100
We might actually be able to do something,

12:09.100 --> 12:09.950
right?

12:10.500 --> 12:12.430
I still think it's inappropriate.

12:12.620 --> 12:13.580
Gao Ran.

12:14.390 --> 12:16.250
Let's think about it from another angle.

12:16.250 --> 12:19.060
We received a betrothal gift of
500 taels of gold.

12:19.140 --> 12:20.540
That's 500 taels of gold!

12:20.580 --> 12:21.670
With this money,

12:21.670 --> 12:23.310
we can support the private school,

12:23.310 --> 12:24.220
right?

12:24.860 --> 12:25.580
Am I right?

12:26.390 --> 12:27.670
Right?

12:28.550 --> 12:30.950
Gao Ran, that's 500 taels of gold.

12:54.040 --> 12:56.440
She hasn't even entered the residence yet,

12:56.580 --> 12:59.880
but the Three Elders have already
sent their test.

13:03.310 --> 13:04.190
Look at this.

13:06.150 --> 13:06.820
Fan Yun.

13:07.310 --> 13:08.500
These gifts from the 3 families—

13:08.500 --> 13:10.300
how do you plan to deal with them?

13:20.190 --> 13:21.660
The meaning of a gift

13:21.950 --> 13:23.540
doesn't lie in receiving,

13:23.850 --> 13:24.880
but in giving.

13:26.070 --> 13:27.460
Since the Three Elders are
showing such kindness,

13:27.460 --> 13:29.100
if I were to send these back,

13:29.100 --> 13:31.100
wouldn't that be rejecting their goodwill?

13:31.100 --> 13:32.100
Besides,

13:32.580 --> 13:33.670
I've never even worn

13:33.670 --> 13:35.730
such expensive silk brocade before.

13:36.860 --> 13:38.310
So you mean...

13:38.580 --> 13:40.220
I mean...

13:42.220 --> 13:43.220
Just wait and see.

13:57.910 --> 13:59.490
♪ Spring winds, autumn rain ♪

13:59.520 --> 14:01.020
♪ Flowers bloom for a single season ♪

14:01.080 --> 14:03.170
♪ Fallen petals turn into mud ♪

14:03.190 --> 14:05.150
♪ Nurturing all living things ♪

14:05.840 --> 14:08.470
♪ Never once asking for
even a single cent ♪

14:09.870 --> 14:12.230
♪ Yet willing, in the name of the clouds ♪

14:12.250 --> 14:13.830
♪ To ignite myself ♪

14:13.860 --> 14:15.900
♪ For the people under heaven ♪

14:16.190 --> 14:18.420
♪ Bright moon, clear breeze ♪

14:18.450 --> 14:22.410
♪ Accompany a heart without dust ♪

14:23.250 --> 14:24.820
♪ All the noise and chaos ♪

14:24.840 --> 14:26.490
♪ The rises and falls of life ♪

14:26.520 --> 14:28.480
♪ What does hardship matter? ♪

14:28.500 --> 14:30.920
♪ In the moment of looking back ♪

14:31.140 --> 14:34.500
♪ This life is worth it ♪

14:34.770 --> 14:37.280
♪ When longing for dawn ♪

14:37.310 --> 14:41.170
♪ Who are the dream-walkers? ♪

14:41.200 --> 14:43.470
♪ Facing the light ♪

14:43.740 --> 14:47.430
♪ Singing a long song along the way ♪

14:47.460 --> 14:50.030
♪ I am willing to become ♪

14:50.060 --> 14:51.680
♪ A long-lasting lantern ♪

14:51.700 --> 14:53.740
♪ Lighting the path ahead ♪

14:53.770 --> 14:56.250
♪ Bypassing right and wrong ♪

14:56.280 --> 14:59.990
♪ Prejudice and fanaticism ♪

15:00.020 --> 15:02.730
♪ Until this road ♪

15:02.770 --> 15:04.450
♪ Has no more obstacles ♪

15:04.480 --> 15:06.640
♪ Time flows like water ♪

15:06.660 --> 15:13.160
♪ Not wasting years of perseverance ♪

15:22.160 --> 15:24.830
♪ I am willing to become ♪

15:24.850 --> 15:26.480
♪ The countless lanterns ♪

15:26.500 --> 15:28.490
♪ Lighting the path ahead ♪

15:28.520 --> 15:31.030
♪ Warming the world ♪

15:31.060 --> 15:34.780
♪ Flickering like a galaxy of stars ♪

15:34.800 --> 15:37.280
♪ Looking at this scenery ♪

15:37.300 --> 15:39.210
♪ Still like in youth ♪

15:39.240 --> 15:41.340
♪ Eyes clear and pure ♪

15:41.360 --> 15:43.880
♪ Mountains and seas change over time ♪

15:43.910 --> 15:48.820
♪ Someone will remember ♪

15:50.070 --> 15:54.360
♪ As long as the heart's light remains ♪

15:53.430 --> 15:54.460
Master.

15:54.990 --> 16:02.890
♪ There won't be loneliness ♪

15:55.070 --> 15:57.150
She's wearing our silk brocade—

15:57.150 --> 16:02.010
a single-layer robe embroidered with
a golden "double happiness" butterfly pattern.

16:03.600 --> 16:05.580
She's wearing our plain Jiang silk—

16:05.580 --> 16:06.860
a stone-blue Kesi brocade ceremonial skirt

16:06.860 --> 16:11.190
embroidered with auspicious cloud,
golden bat, and golden dragon patterns.

16:11.240 --> 16:12.510
She's wearing our Kesi
golden "double happiness"

16:12.510 --> 16:16.640
and butterfly pattern front-opening jacket
with an embroidered collar.

16:25.370 --> 16:27.420
Her Ladyship

16:28.980 --> 16:31.390
sure knows how to be impartial.

16:58.150 --> 16:59.970
I've waited for 4 whole hours.

17:00.550 --> 17:02.430
How much longer do I have to wait?

17:35.950 --> 17:37.410
This is so uncomfortable.

18:09.870 --> 18:11.430
So this is what the inside of

18:12.430 --> 18:14.030
the Qi Residence looks like.

18:32.140 --> 18:34.030
So many rare treasures—

18:35.090 --> 18:37.020
how much money must they have cost?

18:41.450 --> 18:42.560
As a mayor,

18:42.960 --> 18:45.500
he ignores the livelihood and safety
of the common people

18:45.500 --> 18:46.570
yet lives such an extravagant life

18:46.570 --> 18:48.040
in his residence.

18:48.800 --> 18:49.680
I'm so mad.

18:52.360 --> 18:52.990
My Lord.

18:53.020 --> 18:54.060
If the Three Elders find out

18:54.060 --> 18:55.640
that you didn't go to your wife's room

18:55.640 --> 18:57.200
on your wedding night...

18:57.230 --> 18:58.560
So what if they find out?

18:59.060 --> 19:00.900
The matters I handle every day

19:00.950 --> 19:02.460
are all important matters.

19:02.460 --> 19:04.540
-Each one concerns our state and people.
-The mayor?

19:04.540 --> 19:05.870
How can I be distracted?

19:06.970 --> 19:09.430
Then, about tomorrow's morning meeting...

19:10.280 --> 19:11.710
Of course I won't go.

19:17.300 --> 19:18.700
So he...

19:19.020 --> 19:20.700
J-Just left?

19:36.660 --> 19:38.320
My Lady, please have some tea.

19:41.530 --> 19:43.820
[Suyin, Maid of Qi Residence]

19:45.430 --> 19:46.480
You...

19:46.510 --> 19:47.870
Who are you?

19:48.540 --> 19:49.670
My name is Suyin.

19:49.670 --> 19:52.000
I've been appointed to serve you, My Lady.

19:55.770 --> 19:56.870
I see.

20:01.740 --> 20:03.190
It's okay, it's okay. Come on, get up.

20:03.190 --> 20:04.120
I deserve to die!

20:04.420 --> 20:05.180
I'm sorry!

20:05.200 --> 20:06.330
I didn't mean to!

20:06.360 --> 20:07.890
Please forgive me, My Lady.

20:09.060 --> 20:10.020
It's okay.

20:10.270 --> 20:12.330
I'll just wipe it clean myself later.

20:12.870 --> 20:13.410
Come on,

20:13.700 --> 20:14.390
get up.

20:14.750 --> 20:16.310
You don't blame me, My Lady?

20:16.330 --> 20:17.590
Why should I blame you?

20:18.110 --> 20:19.170
It's just a teacup.

20:19.470 --> 20:21.190
Doesn't this happen all the time?

20:21.190 --> 20:22.450
What's there to blame?

20:23.390 --> 20:23.910
But...

20:23.980 --> 20:24.630
But

20:25.150 --> 20:26.200
from now on, with me,

20:26.200 --> 20:27.120
you don't have to be

20:27.120 --> 20:28.120
so formal.

20:28.140 --> 20:29.240
You can be more relaxed.

20:29.240 --> 20:31.520
You are truly the best lady I've ever met.

20:33.480 --> 20:34.790
So you mean

20:35.500 --> 20:38.020
there are other ladies in this residence?

20:38.780 --> 20:40.220
No, no, absolutely not.

20:40.220 --> 20:42.110
His Lordship only has you as
his one and only wife.

20:42.110 --> 20:44.260
You are unprecedented in all these years—

20:44.260 --> 20:46.430
absolutely one of a kind, utterly unique,

20:46.430 --> 20:48.670
the only lady
His Lordship has ever fallen for.

20:48.670 --> 20:50.950
A message from His Lordship.

20:52.920 --> 20:53.770
My Lady,

20:54.810 --> 20:57.160
His Lordship is tied up with
important matters tonight

20:57.160 --> 20:59.290
and will not return to the room to rest.

20:59.540 --> 21:02.410
He specifically sent me here to tell you.

21:06.370 --> 21:07.030
Got it.

21:07.670 --> 21:08.320
Then,

21:08.350 --> 21:09.650
I will take my leave.

21:20.540 --> 21:23.900
So the rumors I heard before
about the mayor keeping away from women

21:23.900 --> 21:25.180
turn out to be true.

21:38.140 --> 21:39.410
Being the mayor

21:39.440 --> 21:40.810
is really easy.

21:42.430 --> 21:43.430
You all may leave.

21:51.300 --> 21:53.700
Even my wife was chosen by
the Three Elders.

21:53.870 --> 21:55.400
How should I get rid of them?

21:55.780 --> 21:58.840
They'll only oppose
what I'm going to do next even more.

22:01.990 --> 22:03.280
Suyin,

22:03.300 --> 22:05.130
do you think

22:05.460 --> 22:06.720
the mayor

22:07.280 --> 22:08.880
will come to our place today?

22:10.220 --> 22:12.110
According to Attendant Wei,

22:12.110 --> 22:12.980
His Lordship

22:13.000 --> 22:15.260
probably won't come back to sleep
these few days.

22:15.260 --> 22:18.520
How am I supposed to start teaching
if he doesn't come back?

22:19.660 --> 22:20.610
I see.

22:24.540 --> 22:25.340
Alright then.

22:30.830 --> 22:32.600
Suyin, why don't you

22:32.780 --> 22:34.900
tell me something about the mayor?

22:35.610 --> 22:36.890
You entered the residence earlier than me.

22:36.890 --> 22:38.420
You must know more than I do.

22:40.470 --> 22:41.300
Come on. Don't just stand there.

22:41.300 --> 22:42.410
Sit down and talk.

22:42.440 --> 22:43.480
I wouldn't dare.

22:44.220 --> 22:45.540
Come on, sit down.

22:45.980 --> 22:47.300
Haven't I told you

22:47.300 --> 22:48.410
that when you're with me,

22:48.410 --> 22:50.060
you don't have to be so formal?

22:50.060 --> 22:50.990
Be more relaxed.

22:51.190 --> 22:51.870
Go ahead.

22:57.220 --> 22:58.220
Look,

22:58.950 --> 23:00.460
as the mayor's new bride,

23:00.780 --> 23:02.020
I haven't seen my husband

23:02.020 --> 23:03.630
for 5 days in a row.

23:05.870 --> 23:07.390
I suppose there's no one

23:07.870 --> 23:10.300
more miserable than me in this world.

23:12.250 --> 23:13.790
After coming of age,

23:14.190 --> 23:16.560
His Lordship has been very perfunctory
in official matters.

23:16.560 --> 23:18.690
He rarely participates in
important state affairs,

23:18.690 --> 23:19.890
but loves to have fun.

23:20.390 --> 23:21.710
He loves most to

23:21.730 --> 23:23.000
drink and have cricket fighting

23:23.000 --> 23:24.400
in the residence for fun.

23:29.470 --> 23:31.860
If you can have fun
along with him, My Lady,

23:32.020 --> 23:33.830
it'll definitely please His Lordship

23:33.830 --> 23:34.980
greatly.

23:40.760 --> 23:41.950
His Lordship once said

23:41.950 --> 23:43.740
that these are all for the inspiration

23:43.740 --> 23:45.270
needed for poetry writing.

23:47.980 --> 23:49.150
That's what he said?

23:52.740 --> 23:54.940
He's really good at inventing excuses.

23:55.830 --> 23:57.220
A-Actually, His Lordship

23:57.220 --> 23:58.910
isn't always like this.

23:59.220 --> 24:01.670
I see that he usually loves studying
quite a bit.

24:01.670 --> 24:04.200
He often reads alone in the study.

24:06.950 --> 24:07.980
In the study?

24:09.730 --> 24:12.450
Come catch me!

24:12.470 --> 24:13.470
I'm here!

24:19.160 --> 24:20.420
There's someone here.

24:24.050 --> 24:25.080
I got you!

24:26.220 --> 24:27.480
Let me feel who you are.

24:28.500 --> 24:29.740
Why are you so chubby?

24:35.030 --> 24:35.780
Wei Zhu.

24:36.470 --> 24:38.070
Why do you have a beard today?

24:39.760 --> 24:40.910
Let me see.

24:50.470 --> 24:52.000
I said I didn't want to play,

24:52.720 --> 24:54.520
but Wei Zhu insisted that I play.

25:29.500 --> 25:31.960
This person has been
wandering around here.

25:32.260 --> 25:33.720
What is he doing?

25:36.360 --> 25:37.360
Sir,

25:40.050 --> 25:42.190
do you need any help?

25:43.880 --> 25:44.600
No.

25:46.120 --> 25:46.780
Alright then.

25:46.780 --> 25:47.490
Wait.

25:50.190 --> 25:53.120
Can you take me to the Qilin Pavilion?

25:53.150 --> 25:54.250
Qilin Pavilion?

25:58.740 --> 26:01.460
So you were just lost, Sir.

26:01.460 --> 26:02.430
Of course not.

26:03.910 --> 26:04.980
Stop talking nonsense.

26:04.980 --> 26:06.910
Are you going to lead the way or not?

26:11.950 --> 26:12.680
Come with me.

26:14.590 --> 26:15.300
This way.

26:16.190 --> 26:17.710
I told you it was this way.

26:21.350 --> 26:23.200
This is Qilin Pavilion.

26:23.800 --> 26:25.210
Basically all the books you want

26:25.210 --> 26:26.650
can be found here.

26:27.860 --> 26:29.660
Should I thank you or something?

26:30.350 --> 26:32.030
I told you I could find the way.

26:35.870 --> 26:37.240
I told you,

26:37.350 --> 26:38.500
if it's more than 30 paces away,

26:38.500 --> 26:39.900
you're bound to get lost.

26:45.180 --> 26:46.100
[Go Tactics]

26:47.690 --> 26:50.750
Weren't you coming to Qilin Pavilion
to look for a book?

26:55.190 --> 26:55.760
Yes.

26:56.670 --> 26:58.840
I happened to come to Qilin Pavilion
to borrow a book.

26:57.100 --> 26:58.330
[Wei Ying, Commander of
the Guardian Corps]

26:59.040 --> 27:01.310
I was lucky enough to
have run into this gentleman today.

27:01.310 --> 27:02.660
He brought me in.

27:03.380 --> 27:05.140
Did he bring you in,

27:05.260 --> 27:06.950
or the other way around?

27:09.180 --> 27:10.140
Wei Ying!

27:14.830 --> 27:15.430
By the way,

27:15.780 --> 27:17.110
what's your name?

27:19.430 --> 27:20.300
My name is

27:21.220 --> 27:21.880
Fan Yun.

27:24.930 --> 27:25.990
-Fan Yun?
-Fan Yun?

27:29.700 --> 27:30.160
My Lady.

27:31.250 --> 27:33.540
I am Wei Ying,
Commander of the Left Guardian Corps.

27:33.540 --> 27:34.150
And this is...

27:34.150 --> 27:35.630
Yan Jiang, Assistant Officer of
the Bureau of Affairs.

27:35.630 --> 27:38.030
I'm also the son of your uncle,
Lord Fan Hui.

27:39.800 --> 27:41.760
So we are all family.

27:42.260 --> 27:43.480
Yes, exactly.

27:44.190 --> 27:46.420
Then thank you both
for lending me the book today.

27:46.420 --> 27:48.470
I will study it carefully when I get back.

27:48.470 --> 27:49.800
-Alright.
-Sure. Sure.

27:49.830 --> 27:51.590
Well then, I'll take my leave.

27:51.590 --> 27:52.500
Take care, My Lady.

27:52.500 --> 27:53.100
Goodbye.

27:58.500 --> 27:59.430
So...

27:59.650 --> 28:01.340
This is the mayor's wife,

28:01.370 --> 28:02.850
Lord Fan Qi's daughter?

28:07.320 --> 28:08.630
It's rare to see you

28:08.740 --> 28:10.260
being so kind to a woman.

28:13.060 --> 28:14.860
Well, I'm not like you, Lord Wei.

28:16.110 --> 28:18.240
You always have women flocking to you.

28:54.430 --> 28:55.760
So inside Qi Residence,

28:56.080 --> 28:57.880
there's such a beautiful place.

28:58.310 --> 29:00.510
No wonder everyone wants to get in here.

29:59.740 --> 30:03.060
♪ Watch how flowers bloom and wither ♪

30:03.640 --> 30:07.150
♪ Count how many springs
and autumns pass ♪

30:07.490 --> 30:09.490
♪ Why the sighs and regrets? ♪

30:11.740 --> 30:12.460
I...

30:13.390 --> 30:15.060
I didn't mean to pick it.

30:15.890 --> 30:19.200
♪ Lovers wait a lifetime ♪

30:17.700 --> 30:18.430
Anyway,

30:19.350 --> 30:20.500
it's yours now.

30:19.850 --> 30:22.990
♪ Love cannot be cut away ♪

30:23.450 --> 30:26.240
♪ How to let go? ♪

30:25.300 --> 30:26.110
Thanks.

30:42.350 --> 30:45.680
Where's the Go manual
that was still on the table a while ago?

30:45.870 --> 30:47.980
You're the great Commander of
the Left Left Guardian Corps,

30:47.980 --> 30:49.640
yet you're making a fuss over a Go manual?

30:49.640 --> 30:51.680
That's no ordinary Go manual.

30:51.700 --> 30:53.460
It holds the mayor's secrets.

30:53.930 --> 30:55.090
Secrets?

30:55.120 --> 30:56.640
What secrets?

30:57.960 --> 30:58.830
It records

30:59.220 --> 31:00.930
the mayor's personal notes
on food, drink, and entertainment,

31:00.930 --> 31:01.660
as well as...

31:02.740 --> 31:04.010
All the bad things he said
about each official.

31:04.010 --> 31:04.930
What?

31:05.250 --> 31:07.910
H-He wrote down bad things
in a little notebook?

31:08.630 --> 31:10.460
Then... If the old scholars find out
about this,

31:10.460 --> 31:11.630
they'll never stop nagging him about it.

31:11.630 --> 31:12.160
Exactly.

31:12.780 --> 31:14.240
Don't even get me started.

31:14.500 --> 31:16.980
I, Wei Ying, am the grand Commander
of the Left Guardian Corps,

31:16.980 --> 31:17.670
and you are

31:17.670 --> 31:20.630
the youngest official
in the history of the Bureau of Affairs.

31:20.630 --> 31:22.430
We should both have bright futures.

31:22.430 --> 31:23.300
Yet we end up

31:23.980 --> 31:26.150
idling around in this place every day

31:26.150 --> 31:27.410
and wasting our youth.

31:27.870 --> 31:28.540
Well,

31:28.950 --> 31:30.870
since the mayor just got married,

31:30.870 --> 31:34.070
maybe his wife will be able to
keep him in check from now on.

31:34.260 --> 31:35.320
Are you really sure

31:35.680 --> 31:37.740
that lady can keep the mayor in check?

31:39.910 --> 31:40.700
I hope so.

31:48.780 --> 31:49.500
Sir.

31:50.150 --> 31:50.700
Sir?

31:52.930 --> 31:53.780
You

31:53.800 --> 31:55.640
still haven't finished reading yet?

31:55.640 --> 31:56.640
I'm not in a hurry.

32:00.590 --> 32:02.680
Maybe you should hurry up, Sir.

32:03.020 --> 32:04.590
It's getting dark.

32:10.190 --> 32:13.430
I still don't know who you are,
flower-admiring gentleman.

32:13.430 --> 32:14.300
How about this?

32:14.300 --> 32:16.260
Once I make tea
with these phoenix flowers,

32:16.260 --> 32:17.670
I'll definitely let you taste it first

32:17.670 --> 32:18.600
as a return gift.

32:20.670 --> 32:21.670
My name is...

32:24.250 --> 32:25.310
My name is Wei Ying.

32:26.500 --> 32:27.300
Wei?

32:27.950 --> 32:29.020
You are Wei Ying?

32:34.210 --> 32:37.070
I'm Wei Ying, Commander of
the Left Guardian Corps.

32:37.350 --> 32:39.220
This person is dressed in a noble-woven

32:39.220 --> 32:40.750
cross-collared wide robe,

32:40.980 --> 32:43.390
wearing a pure white
mutton-fat jade pendant

32:43.390 --> 32:45.020
and ice-silk silver thread ribbons,

32:45.020 --> 32:47.620
with tiger-patterned Liuhe boots
on his feet.

32:47.630 --> 32:48.700
Only the mayor...

32:49.190 --> 32:50.220
The mayor?

32:52.020 --> 32:53.540
So you are

32:53.540 --> 32:55.600
the famed Commander Wei.

32:55.740 --> 32:57.200
I've heard a lot about you.

32:57.220 --> 33:00.310
They say you are the mayor's favorite.

33:00.500 --> 33:01.910
It's an honor to meet you today.

33:01.910 --> 33:03.970
You truly live up to your reputation.

33:04.570 --> 33:06.910
Truly a great "genius."

33:12.910 --> 33:13.900
And who are you?

33:15.670 --> 33:16.430
I...

33:19.690 --> 33:20.690
My name is Fan Yun.

33:28.370 --> 33:29.260
So you are my...

33:30.160 --> 33:31.220
I mean, the mayor's

33:31.290 --> 33:32.200
wife?

33:36.110 --> 33:37.390
I've only entered the residence

33:37.390 --> 33:39.050
and already met you, Lord Wei.

33:39.540 --> 33:40.950
How fortunate.

33:41.830 --> 33:44.150
Being near you, it seems

33:44.150 --> 33:46.430
I can feel some of the mayor's...

33:47.980 --> 33:50.410
The mayor's...

33:51.010 --> 33:52.090
Radiance.

33:52.980 --> 33:53.590
Radiance.

33:56.740 --> 33:58.190
What kind of radiance?

33:58.190 --> 34:00.300
Just... The mayor's

34:00.300 --> 34:01.670
dazzling radiance!

34:01.670 --> 34:03.300
The mayor's brilliance shines everywhere,

34:03.300 --> 34:04.880
and we can all feel it.

34:07.840 --> 34:09.540
I have important matters to attend to,

34:09.540 --> 34:10.739
so I'll take my leave.

34:10.880 --> 34:11.810
Thanks for this.

34:37.750 --> 34:39.570
Saying he's Wei Ying?

34:40.790 --> 34:42.719
Why would he call himself Wei Ying?

34:50.909 --> 34:52.980
The two of them have finally met.

34:54.100 --> 34:55.230
Indeed they have.

34:57.180 --> 34:58.370
Married for days

34:58.660 --> 35:00.140
and nowhere to be seen.

35:00.140 --> 35:02.430
It seems the mayor's wife

35:02.430 --> 35:03.560
is nothing special.

35:05.950 --> 35:09.190
Better to find someone else soon.

35:13.820 --> 35:15.480
I've started looking. I have.

35:17.870 --> 35:19.660
I beg to differ.

35:20.950 --> 35:22.310
Look, those two

35:22.310 --> 35:23.950
just got married

35:23.950 --> 35:25.620
and aren't very familiar with
each other yet.

35:25.620 --> 35:27.850
If they get to know each other more,

35:28.020 --> 35:30.710
maybe they'll become inseparable.

35:32.350 --> 35:33.680
Let's wait a bit longer.

35:35.500 --> 35:36.500
Wait a bit longer.

36:19.800 --> 36:20.880
Lord Wei?

36:23.900 --> 36:25.900
Please don't let anyone else see me.

36:26.430 --> 36:27.600
Dressed like this, sneaking around—

36:27.600 --> 36:29.220
where are you going?

36:29.660 --> 36:30.750
I...

36:33.710 --> 36:34.670
I wanted to

36:35.060 --> 36:36.590
sneak out of the residence.

36:37.910 --> 36:38.660
How dare you?

36:39.460 --> 36:41.620
How could the mayor's wife
leave the mansion freely?

36:41.620 --> 36:43.680
Didn't your maids tell you the rules?

36:44.650 --> 36:46.440
I have no choice.

36:47.020 --> 36:47.950
Lord Wei.

36:47.950 --> 36:49.060
You don't know,

36:49.060 --> 36:50.660
it's been many days
since I entered the residence,

36:50.660 --> 36:52.590
and I still haven't seen the mayor.

36:53.230 --> 36:55.500
I know the mayor must be very busy

36:55.500 --> 36:56.500
and diligent,

36:57.100 --> 36:58.020
so

36:58.310 --> 37:00.140
I was thinking when I see him
for the first time,

37:00.140 --> 37:01.140
I could give him a gift

37:01.140 --> 37:02.200
to make him happy.

37:03.430 --> 37:05.890
What thing can't be found
in the Qi Residence

37:06.180 --> 37:07.830
that you have to go outside to buy?

37:07.830 --> 37:09.540
The things in the Qi Residence

37:09.540 --> 37:11.180
are indeed abundant and good,

37:11.180 --> 37:13.840
but the mayor definitely
won't find them novel.

37:13.950 --> 37:14.870
But

37:14.870 --> 37:16.270
it's different outside.

37:16.550 --> 37:17.680
There are many

37:17.750 --> 37:18.620
fun and entertaining things

37:18.620 --> 37:20.120
on the bustling streets.

37:20.270 --> 37:21.540
Oh, right, there are also

37:21.540 --> 37:24.310
countless strange and novel stories.

37:28.060 --> 37:29.290
Lord Wei,

37:29.950 --> 37:31.470
I beg you.

37:31.490 --> 37:32.940
Please be generous

37:33.270 --> 37:34.180
and let me out,

37:34.430 --> 37:35.100
okay?

37:35.830 --> 37:37.090
The bustling streets,

37:37.830 --> 37:39.360
strange and novel stories?

37:40.910 --> 37:41.660
How fun

37:42.060 --> 37:43.320
and how novel are they?

37:46.410 --> 37:47.810
Well,

37:47.860 --> 37:48.820
they are just very fun

37:48.820 --> 37:50.010
and very novel.

37:56.440 --> 37:58.100
Considering your sincerity,

37:58.180 --> 37:59.440
I might just let you go.

38:00.310 --> 38:01.460
Really?

38:01.640 --> 38:03.370
But you have to take me with you.

38:12.040 --> 38:13.570
This is the East Market.

38:13.600 --> 38:15.550
Nobles often gather here.

38:15.660 --> 38:16.330
Look,

38:16.500 --> 38:19.830
there are brush shops, taverns,
jewelry stores,

38:19.830 --> 38:20.980
and so on.

38:20.980 --> 38:21.950
In short,

38:21.950 --> 38:23.430
no matter how rare the item is,

38:23.430 --> 38:24.140
you can

38:24.140 --> 38:25.270
find it here.

38:28.200 --> 38:32.960
[West Market]

38:34.350 --> 38:36.870
And this is the West Market.

38:37.400 --> 38:39.560
Commoners usually make a living here.

38:39.580 --> 38:41.340
The environment here used to be very poor,

38:41.340 --> 38:44.110
but it has improved a bit
in the last couple of years.

38:44.110 --> 38:45.280
So these shops

38:45.310 --> 38:46.930
opened up one after another.

38:50.710 --> 38:52.590
Could it be that the sight

38:53.060 --> 38:55.230
before the mayor has touched him?

39:03.750 --> 39:05.310
Teachable.

39:08.620 --> 39:09.870
Well, Lord Wei,

39:09.870 --> 39:11.830
you command the Guardian Corps after all.

39:11.830 --> 39:13.100
Why do you look like

39:13.100 --> 39:14.390
you've never

39:14.390 --> 39:16.120
been out on the streets before?

39:19.040 --> 39:20.540
I'm usually busy with official duties

39:20.540 --> 39:23.460
and rarely have the leisure
to stroll around the market.

39:23.460 --> 39:25.260
Well, Lord Wei, you may not know,

39:25.710 --> 39:28.430
this street is for leisure to you,

39:29.180 --> 39:30.620
but to many people,

39:30.980 --> 39:32.310
it's their livelihood.

39:35.330 --> 39:37.460
Aren't you thinking of buying a gift
for the mayor?

39:37.460 --> 39:39.060
I think these two are not bad.

39:41.980 --> 39:42.690
Lord Wei,

39:42.980 --> 39:44.970
don't you want to check out
the West Market more?

39:44.970 --> 39:46.360
They all have a hard time.

39:46.360 --> 39:49.020
Isn't this the joy of
strolling down the street?

39:50.950 --> 39:51.670
However,

39:51.990 --> 39:53.670
compared to the West Market,
this East Market

39:53.670 --> 39:55.470
is indeed much more prosperous.

39:55.760 --> 39:56.890
You know your stuff.

39:57.840 --> 40:01.100
It's not too much to ask you
to stroll with me for a bit, is it?

40:01.460 --> 40:02.430
No, no.

40:02.430 --> 40:03.660
Not at all.

40:03.660 --> 40:04.830
I'm best

40:04.830 --> 40:05.910
at this.

40:07.200 --> 40:07.840
Let's go.

40:11.310 --> 40:12.460
I knew it.

40:14.950 --> 40:17.350
Since you've got so much money
to squander,

40:17.660 --> 40:18.660
I'll help you out.

40:19.870 --> 40:20.660
Sorry.

40:20.660 --> 40:22.430
I'm really sorry, Mayor.

40:22.710 --> 40:24.070
I had no choice

40:24.390 --> 40:27.140
but to take a little "commission"
off the top.

40:27.390 --> 40:30.080
Just think of it as taking from the people
and using it for the people.

40:30.080 --> 40:31.910
If you want to blame someone,
blame Lord Lyu.

40:31.910 --> 40:32.700
Who would have thought

40:32.700 --> 40:35.360
he was paying me the gift money
in installments?

40:46.350 --> 40:47.460
This way,

40:47.640 --> 40:50.520
I'll have enough for next month's rent
for the private school,

40:50.520 --> 40:53.120
Father and Gao Ran's
living expenses,

40:54.100 --> 40:56.750
and the students' ink and brushes.

40:57.830 --> 41:00.750
I can even renovate the private school.

41:01.370 --> 41:03.660
But when I have money in the future,

41:03.870 --> 41:05.600
I will definitely pay you back.

41:06.100 --> 41:07.230
I promise.

41:09.100 --> 41:10.310
Wait for me!

41:14.810 --> 41:16.610
[Huan'e House]

41:20.870 --> 41:22.470
Lord Wei, do you want to go in?

41:24.660 --> 41:25.990
You have acquaintances

41:26.140 --> 41:27.740
in this kind of place as well?

41:30.100 --> 41:31.100
Who knows?

41:31.620 --> 41:32.380
Follow me.

41:32.380 --> 41:33.660
Please come in, guests!

41:33.660 --> 41:35.390
Come on, two VIPs!

41:38.470 --> 41:41.030
This place is called Huan'e House.

41:41.140 --> 41:42.580
It has only been established
for a few years,

41:42.580 --> 41:45.240
but it's already the top tavern
in Ling'an City.

41:45.370 --> 41:47.100
It connects to the central road
in the front

41:47.100 --> 41:48.910
and the river passing through the city
in the back.

41:48.910 --> 41:51.830
Whether you ride a horse, walk,
or come by boat,

41:51.830 --> 41:53.430
it's extremely convenient.

41:53.430 --> 41:56.140
Therefore, the composition of
the coming and going people is complex.

41:56.140 --> 41:58.180
All factions in Ling'an

41:58.180 --> 41:59.580
and all channels and news

41:59.750 --> 42:01.180
converge here.

42:10.130 --> 42:10.880
Wait for it.

42:10.910 --> 42:11.680
The show

42:11.700 --> 42:12.780
is about to start.

42:14.630 --> 42:16.430
Lord Wei, have some water first.

42:25.020 --> 42:27.660
Bravo! Bravo!

42:34.100 --> 42:35.160
Welcome everyone,

42:35.540 --> 42:37.410
to Huan'e House.

42:38.270 --> 42:39.530
Our Huan'e House

42:39.830 --> 42:41.830
is different from ordinary taverns.

42:41.830 --> 42:44.050
We sell both talent and news.

42:44.320 --> 42:46.420
This is what makes our boss, Miss Hu Die,

42:46.420 --> 42:47.790
so remarkable.

42:48.460 --> 42:49.710
Only those who spend enough money

42:49.710 --> 42:51.390
to enter her boudoir

42:51.740 --> 42:53.300
can get the news.

42:53.790 --> 42:55.630
This is the famous

42:55.650 --> 42:57.450
"Seating Ceremony" in Ling'an.

42:58.180 --> 42:59.100
Interesting.

42:59.460 --> 42:59.870
Isn't it?

42:59.870 --> 43:01.460
This is my first time seeing an auction,

43:01.460 --> 43:02.620
and it's actually for

43:02.620 --> 43:03.980
a chance to ask questions face-to-face.

43:03.980 --> 43:04.550
How is it?

43:04.910 --> 43:06.510
Isn't it more fun than the Qi Residence?

43:06.510 --> 43:07.200
Lord Wei.

43:07.460 --> 43:08.800
You can give it a try too.

43:09.060 --> 43:10.660
Is there anything you are curious about,

43:10.660 --> 43:11.830
or anyone?

43:14.210 --> 43:16.470
How could there be anything I don't know?

43:17.760 --> 43:18.960
Let's keep watching.

43:19.230 --> 43:21.440
If you don't bid,
how can I get my commission?

43:21.440 --> 43:22.260
10 taels.

43:22.290 --> 43:23.320
I bid 30 taels.

43:24.950 --> 43:26.140
I bid 50 taels.

43:29.750 --> 43:30.870
80 taels.

43:33.350 --> 43:34.680
I bid 100 taels.

43:36.430 --> 43:37.580
120 taels.

43:42.280 --> 43:43.660
150 taels.

43:44.850 --> 43:45.730
300 taels!

43:48.100 --> 43:50.560
Let's see who dares to
compete with me today.

43:51.270 --> 43:52.460
300 taels...

43:53.790 --> 43:54.580
Lord Wei.

43:54.900 --> 43:56.050
You bid 300 taels.

43:56.450 --> 43:58.540
I don't think anyone would dare
to compete with you.

43:58.540 --> 44:01.390
Anyone else bidding against
this gentleman?

44:02.350 --> 44:03.310
No matter who bids higher,

44:03.310 --> 44:04.430
I'll double it.

44:22.420 --> 44:26.620
[Lou Qiyan, Owner of Juyun Pavilion]
